I made this as more of a concept map. I want more large/tactical/realistic maps in CS:S. If you play it you will realise it isn't perfect mapping. I'm hoping a more experienced mapper will take this idea and perfect it. So no hard feelings for ripping it off :D

Canadian Ninja
